", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-27T11:10:35Z to 2025-06-27T11:21:35Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-27 11:10:35+00:00 to 2025-06-27 11:21:35+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["productcatalogservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "shippingservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "adservice-0", "currencyservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-0", "paymentservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["cartservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "frontend-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "memory_usage", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"timeout\", \"timed out\", \"i/o timeout\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"connection error\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"网络连接超时和握手超时，导致支付服务无法响应\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout 和 timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"作为调用方，在调用支付服务时遇到连接超时问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有错误日志均来自frontend服务，显示在调用/cart/checkout接口时出现支付服务连接问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点总结：\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：所有错误都来自frontend服务，在调用`/cart/checkout`接口时发生\n2. **关键错误类型**：主要涉及两种错误模式：\n   - **i/o timeout**：网络连接超时（IP: 10.233.55.4:50051）\n   - **server handshake timeout**：服务器握手超时\n3. **公共嫌疑人**：从错误链分析，问题出现在frontend调用支付服务的过程中\n4. **故障影响范围**：影响所有frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n5. **时间分布**：错误集中在11:11-11:15时间段，但持续到11:21仍有发生\n\n**下一步建议**：需要进一步分析paymentservice的健康状态和网络配置，特别是IP地址10.233.55.4:50051对应的服务实例。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的trace数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从数据中可以清晰地看到异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用paymentservice时出现大量连接超时错误：'dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout'和'timed out waiting for server handshake'，错误状态码14（Unavailable）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice内部调用PaymentService/Charge操作延迟从正常13.68ms激增至23.27秒，延迟倍数高达1700倍，异常频次22次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用CheckoutService/PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常150ms左右激增至22-23秒，延迟倍数超过140倍，导致HTTP 500错误向上传播\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice作为受害者，接收到frontend的PlaceOrder请求后，由于paymentservice不可用，产生大量13状态码错误（内部服务错误）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **根因明确**：paymentservice完全不可用，表现为网络连接超时（i/o timeout）和握手超时\n2. **传播路径**：paymentservice → checkoutservice → frontend，形成典型的错误传播链\n3. **延迟影响**：最严重的延迟出现在checkoutservice内部调用paymentservice的Charge操作（1700倍延迟增长）\n4. **错误类型**：主要是连接层面的Unavailable错误，表明paymentservice可能宕机或网络隔离\n\n根据拓扑关系，paymentservice是最下游的异常服务，是本次故障的根因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面扫描，我发现了多个显著的异常调用链和性能问题。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务集群\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务的所有实例均出现严重的error_ratio和server_error_ratio异常，同时rrt_max和rrt指标大幅飙升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 error_ratio从0.0升至0.15，server_error_ratio从0.0升至0.15，rrt_max从192804.5升至41966725.0(增长198倍)；frontend-1 error_ratio从0.0升至0.21，server_error_ratio从0.0升至0.21，rrt_max从172677.5升至20096992.0(增长116倍)；frontend-2 error_ratio从0.0升至0.21，server_error_ratio从0.0升至0.21，rrt_max从172641.0升至20062019.0(增长115倍)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice-0的rrt_max和rrt指标出现极端异常，响应时间飙升到极高水平\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从143042.5升至33691761.0(增长235倍)，rrt从3803.6升至689107.9(增长180倍)，表明该Pod处理能力严重下降\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08节点\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存可用量显著下降，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes指标异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从7717625856.0降至5149741056.0(下降39.9%)，该节点上运行着redis-cart-0、checkoutservice-0等多个关键服务\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03节点\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率异常下降，node_memory_usage_rate指标变化显著\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate从49.51%降至34.18%(下降36.6%)，表明可能存在内存回收或Pod调度异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice服务集群\",\n      \"reason\": \"paymentservice多个实例的rrt_max和rrt指标出现异常波动\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-2 rrt_max从1654.5升至1350.0(异常下降)，p99值从5333.17升至1482934.6(增长277倍)；paymentservice-0和paymentservice-1也出现类似响应时间异常\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n1. **前端服务严重故障**：frontend服务所有实例均出现高错误率和响应时间飙升\n2. **核心服务性能瓶颈**：checkoutservice-0响应时间极端恶化，可能成为系统瓶颈\n3. **节点资源问题**：aiops-k8s-08节点内存可用量显著下降，可能影响其上运行的关键服务\n4. **支付服务异常**：paymentservice响应时间出现异常波动\n\n这些异常表明系统存在多个层级的性能问题，需要进一步深入分析以确定根本原因。"}
